These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, montecristo, game, ritmeester
City: liverpool, rome, nizza, venice
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, cycling, snowboarding, weightlifting
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, writing, magic-tricks, woodworking
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, daisy, marigold, zinnia
 1. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the aristoff-smoker and the person who growszinnia##2
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is the person who growszinnia##1
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 5. the person who growssunflower is between the aristoff-smoker and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
 7. the person who growsdaisy is the game-smoker##1
 8. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 9. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Cigar           | game | aristoff   | ritmeester | montecristo |
| City   | liverpool      | rome | nizza              | venice |
| Sport   | ice-hockey       | cycling     | weightlifting               | snowboarding    |
| Hobby           | writing        | magic-tricks     | woodworking           | camping       |
| Flower     | daisy | marigold     | sunflower                | zinnia      |

