The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, taxi, trike, scooter
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, traveling, reading, fishing
 1. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 2. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 3. the chaman-smoker is between the person who growstulip and the person driving the taxi##2
 4. the person who likes fuchsia is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 5. the person driving the trike is the chaman-smoker##1
 6. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
 7. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
 8. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
10. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
11. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who growstulip##1
12. the person who growsaconite is the bolivar-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
