There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, spinach, corn, cherry
 1. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
 2. the person who likes ebony is between the mexican and the person eating corn##2
 3. the brazilian is between the person who growsdahlia and the person who growsbellflower##2
 4. the person eating pumpkin is the victorian house##1
 5. the person who likes mauve is the cottage house##1
 6. the brazilian is the person who growsaconite##1
 7. the person eating cherry is the person who growsdahlia##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 9. the brazilian is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
10. the japanese is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
11. the person who likes coral is between the cottage house and the person eating cherry##2
12. the person who likes ebony is between the person eating pumpkin and the person who growsaconite##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Flower      | bellflower      | aconite         | dahlia | iris      |
| House           | cottage | palace | ranch-style | victorian     |
| Nationality   | japanese         | brazilian          | malaysian  | mexican |
| Color         | mauve        | coral  | ebony | black   |
| Food     | spinach    | corn         | cherry     | pumpkin     |

