.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-18::.
City: edinburgh, venice, rome, prague
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, yellow, lavender, ebony
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, punk, jazz, r&b
4 different games are played: whist, chess, poker, canasta
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, iris, daffodil, rose
 1. the fan r&b is between the person playing poker and the person who growsiris##2
 2. the fan r&b is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
 3. the person playing chess is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 4. the fan pop is on the far right##1
 5. the person playing canasta is on the right of the fan jazz##1
 6. the person playing chess is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person who likes ebony##1
 8. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
 9. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
10. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
11. the person traveling to prague is between the person who likes ebony and the person playing whist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |   4    |
| City          | edinburgh  | prague  | venice  | rome   |
| Color   | ebony     | aquamarine | lavender     | yellow |
| Music-Genre           | jazz   | r&b     | punk      | pop   |
| Game         | poker   | canasta    | whist  | chess |
| Flower     | azalea | rose     | iris | daffodil |

