.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-19::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, romance, spy, action
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, watermelon, lime, apricot
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, light-blue, white, mauve
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, backgammon, snooker
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, february, april, may
 1. the person who likes white is the person eating watermelon##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who likes white##1
 3. the person watching romance movies is between the person playing snooker and the person who likes mauve##2
 4. the person who likes mauve is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is between the person watching romance movies and the person who's birthday is in may##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 7. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating raspberry is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person who likes red##1
10. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |       4       |
| Movie-Genre      | action    | romance     | scientific        | spy          |
| Food         | apricot | watermelon   | raspberry        | lime |
| Color           | red   | white | mauve | light-blue      |
| Game   | snooker    | billiard      | mah-jongg          | backgammon        |
| Birthday     | october  | february   | april      | may           |

