.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, turquise, blue, ivory
House: victorian, farmhouse, townhouse, ranch-style
City: berlin, san-francisco, edinburgh, new-york
4 different pets are kept: mouse, dog, rabbit, rat
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, teacher, accountant, engineer
 1. the ranch-style house is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 2. the engineer is between the person traveling to new-york and the owner of the mouse##2
 3. the teacher is between the owner of the dog and the accountant##2
 4. the farmhouse house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 5. the townhouse house is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 6. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
 7. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 8. the townhouse house is the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the teacher is on the left of the accountant##1
10. the person who likes amber is the person traveling to berlin##1
11. the person traveling to berlin is the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Color         | blue  | turquise | ivory | amber |
| House   | ranch-style      | farmhouse   | townhouse      | victorian    |
| City   | san-francisco  | edinburgh | new-york        | berlin     |
| Pet         | mouse  | dog  | rabbit     | rat      |
| Job     | coach | engineer      | teacher   | accountant       |

 